Question: The left image shows a stack of at least four round patties topped with a dollop of white cream and sprinkled with green ring shapes, all on a white dish.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://www.fortheloveofcooking.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/DSC_9910Cheesy-Mashed-Potato-Pancakes.jpg

Right image URL: https://i1.wp.com/www.justputzing.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/DSC_0238b2.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many round patties are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many round patties are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a dollop of white cream on top?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a dollop of white cream on top?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are there green ring shapes sprinkled on top?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are there green ring shapes sprinkled on top?')
ANSWER6=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the dish white?')
ANSWER7=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the dish white?')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} >= 4 and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER4} and {ANSWER6}')
ANSWER9=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} >= 4 and {ANSWER3} and {ANSWER5} and {ANSWER7}')
ANSWER10=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER8} xor {ANSWER9}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER10)
```
